ch.hearc.orlac.data.effect

Class DataEffectCurrent

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.hearc.orlac.data.effect.DataEffect_A
      • ch.hearc.orlac.data.effect.DataEffectCurrent

  • public class DataEffectCurrent
extends DataEffect_A
    Contains the current data effect values.
    The OSC message sended to Pure Data is build with the current values of this class.
    Author:
    chavailm
